VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT enable_https_traffic_only\s*=\s*false
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:enable_https_traffic_only\s*=\s*false|min_tls_version\s*=\s*"TLS1_0" && MISSING:# intentional|# legacy
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects storage accounts that allow unencrypted HTTP access.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Azure Storage Account Without Secure Transfer Required.
